Student_Award_COD_MPN_Data.description: The Financial Award ID for an endorsed PLUS Loan. When the Financial Award ID matches an endorsed PLUS Loan, Workday associates the MPN Certification with that loan. When there's no match, Workday associates the MPN Certification to non-endorsed PLUS Loans based on the Borrower SSN.
